---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<main class="px-8 py-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-mono text-neutral-100 bg-neutral-950 leading-relaxed">

  <h1 class="text-3xl mb-8">Works</h1>

  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl mb-3">The Groundative Treatise · Volume I — Foundation</h2>

    <p class="mb-4">
      The first canonical work of the Groundative Tradition.<br/>
      A descriptive–presential framework of reality.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4">
      It establishes the fundamental laws, principles, and methods of the Groundative system:
      knowledge as presence, truth as coherence, and integrity as the ethic of being.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-6">
      <a href="/pdfs/GROUNDATIVE_TREATISE_VOL_I_FOUNDATION_DIGITAL_ED_2025.pdf"
         target="_blank"
         class="px-5 py-2 border border-neutral-700 text-neutral-100 hover:bg-neutral-800 transition">
         Read / Download PDF
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mt-3">
      © 2025 XYNACT · XYNACT Press · ISBN 978-82-XXXX-XXX-X (pending registration)
    </p>
  </section>

  <hr class="border-neutral-800 my-10"/>

  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl mb-3">Volume II — Application & Praxis</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Forthcoming volume expanding the Groundative method into practice:
      education, art, science, and civic life.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">
      Expected release: 2026.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl mb-3">Volume III — Language & Ontology</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      A deeper articulation of the linguistic and ontological laws
      introduced in Volume I — how word and world cohere.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">
      In development.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="text-2xl mb-3">Other Works</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Additional essays, dialogues, and lectures will be published through
      <a href="https://journal.xynact.com" class="text-neutral-300 underline hover:text-neutral-100">Journal · The Groundative Way</a>
      and <a href="https://press.xynact.com" class="text-neutral-300 underline hover:text-neutral-100">XYNACT Press</a>.
    </p>
  </section>

  <footer class="mt-12 text-xs text-neutral-600 text-center">
    © 2025 XYNACT · What Is, Is · Groundative Tradition
  </footer>
</main>
